WEBVTT

00:06.674 --> 00:09.043
PREVIOUSLY ON
"UNITED STATES OF TARA"...

00:09.077 --> 00:11.112
[ As Alice ]
CHICKEN IS MISSING.

00:11.145 --> 00:12.746
SHE WAS PLAYING
IN THE CORNFIELD,

00:12.780 --> 00:14.748
WHEN SOMETHING UNSPEAKABLE
HAPPENED TO HER.

00:14.782 --> 00:15.749
I KILLED HER.

00:15.783 --> 00:17.551
AND WHO ARE YOU?

00:17.585 --> 00:19.387
I'M BRYCE CRAINE.

00:19.420 --> 00:21.755
THE RELEVANT TERM HERE
IS "ABUSER ALTER."

00:21.789 --> 00:24.292
IT'S A PERSONALITY
MODELED ON A PRIMARY ABUSER --

00:24.325 --> 00:25.759
CARETAKER,
FAMILY MEMBER...

00:25.793 --> 00:26.760
OR A STEPBROTHER.

00:26.794 --> 00:28.162
BRYCE?

00:28.196 --> 00:30.331
