FOR YOUR CUTTING.

00:31.632 --> 00:33.234
ISN'T IT WONDERFUL?

00:33.267 --> 00:34.568
IT'S LIKE...

00:34.602 --> 00:36.337
CHRISTMAS EVERY DAY.

00:36.370 --> 00:39.673
