THAT I NOT HANG AROUND.

00:43.777 --> 00:45.079
YOU EVEN KNOW
WHERE YOU'RE GOING?

00:45.113 --> 00:46.314
YEAH.

00:46.347 --> 00:47.781
I WANT TO MAKE
MY OWN PROBLEMS.

00:47.815 --> 00:49.617
THAT'S MY RIGHT
AS A HUMAN FUCKING BEING.

00:49.650 --> 00:52.086
AND SO I CHOOSE YOU.

00:52.120 --> 00:53.087
BE MY PROBLEM.

00:53.121 --> 00:54.355
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:54.388 --> 00:57.691
THE LITTLE GIRL, THE JEW,
THE PONCHO --

00:57.725 --> 01:00.361
