01:19.147 --> 01:21.782
* HELLO, THERE

01:21.815 --> 01:25.853
* MERRY CHRISTMAS,
HOW'VE YOU BEEN? *

01:27.321 --> 01:29.290
* GEE, IT'S SO GOOD

01:29.323 --> 01:30.391
[ Singsong voice ]
