01:30.424 --> 01:34.828
* TO TALK TO YOU AGAIN

01:34.862 --> 01:36.864
[ CHUCKLES ]

01:36.897 --> 01:41.269
* IT'S BEEN A LONG, LONG TIME

01:41.302 --> 01:43.504
* CAN'T EXPLAIN
WHY YOU'VE CROSSED MY MIND *

01:43.537 --> 01:45.306
[ HUMMING ]

01:45.339 --> 01:49.210
* I GUESS IT'S JUST
TO WISH YOU A MERRY CHRISTMAS *

