02:00.188 --> 02:01.155
* I KNOW IT'S GONNA BE
A LOT OF FUN *

02:01.189 --> 02:04.858
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:04.892 --> 02:09.797
* OH, BY THE WAY,
IT'S SNOWING *

02:11.699 --> 02:15.803
* IT'S BEEN A LONG, LONG TIME

02:15.836 --> 02:19.573
* CAN'T EXPLAIN
WHY YOU'VE CROSSED MY MIND *

02:19.607 --> 02:26.747
* I GUESS IT'S JUST TO SAY,
GEE WHIZ, IT'S CHRISTMAS *

02:26.780 --> 02:30.184
* HAVE A MERRY,
MERRY CHRISTMAS *

02:32.586 --> 02:34.522
[ As Buck ] Psst!

02:34.555 --> 02:35.789
Hey, Max-aroo.

02:35.823 --> 02:37.291
