THINK ABOUT HER.

03:12.360 --> 03:13.327
I WILL -- I GUESS.

03:13.361 --> 03:14.328
UH, LET ME JUST --

03:14.362 --> 03:16.230
OH, SHIT.
HERE HE COMES.

03:16.264 --> 03:19.400
