OF MR. JOHN WAYNE --

03:22.035 --> 03:23.571
PACIFIC VIEW
MEMORIAL PARK,

03:23.604 --> 03:24.938
BAYVIEW TERRACE,
SECTION 575.

03:24.972 --> 03:25.939
