YOU CAN THIS TIME.

04:42.049 --> 04:44.552
I'LL GET HER BACK.
JUST TRUST ME.

04:44.585 --> 04:45.786
Wow.

04:45.819 --> 04:46.887
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

04:46.920 --> 04:48.656
