WE'D HAVE A SLICE.

05:22.756 --> 05:24.525
OH.

05:24.558 --> 05:25.659
[ GASPS ]

05:25.693 --> 05:28.529
1974.

05:28.562 --> 05:31.532
YEAR THEY FOUND THAT SKELETON
IN ETHIOPIA --

05:31.565 --> 05:33.534
CALLED HER "LUCY."

05:33.567 --> 05:37.371
YOUR GRANDFATHER BOUGHT
A SAMSONITE CASE FOR $62,

05:37.405 --> 05:39.907
WHICH WAS VERY EXPENSIVE,
BUT IT HAD WHEELS.

05:39.940 --> 05:42.075
