AROUND ON IT.

05:42.109 --> 05:45.713
HE WANTS ME
TO COME HOME -- DAD.

05:45.746 --> 05:47.815
HE NEEDS HELP, BUT...
[ SIGHS ]

05:47.848 --> 05:49.617
