IF I WANT TO DEAL WITH HER.

05:49.650 --> 05:52.786
DON'T BE SILLY.
SHE'S YOUR MOTHER.

05:52.820 --> 05:55.523
YOU --
YOU HAVE TO LOVE HER,

05:55.556 --> 05:57.725
