YOU THINK SHE IS.

05:57.758 --> 06:01.161
SO...HERE.

06:01.194 --> 06:02.996
YOUR DAD
LOVES FRUITCAKE.

06:03.030 --> 06:05.566
* ROCKIN' IN THE HOLIDAYS

06:05.599 --> 06:07.668
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

06:11.204 --> 06:13.907
[ As Bryce ] DOWN HERE
SPANKING THE MONKEY?

