WHO DO I HAVE TO KILL

06:20.948 --> 06:23.417
TO GET A LITTLE RESPECT
AROUND HERE?

06:23.451 --> 06:25.686
OH, DON'T ACT
LIKE YOU MISS THEM.

06:25.719 --> 06:27.555
I GET THIS DONE,
AND WE'RE BOTH FREE --

06:27.588 --> 06:29.523
NO MORE CRAZY TOWN.

06:29.557 --> 06:31.592
WE GET REAL LIVES.

06:31.625 --> 06:33.861
THE LIFE I WANT
IS WITH MY WIFE.

06:33.894 --> 06:35.729
