06:41.635 --> 06:43.604
NICE HAIRCUT.
STILL BRYCE?

06:43.637 --> 06:45.138
YOU STILL
CHUGGING COCK?

06:45.172 --> 06:46.774
THANKS FOR COMING,
MARSH.

06:46.807 --> 06:48.476
YEAH, NO PROBLEM.
GLAD TO HELP.

06:48.509 --> 06:50.110
