AND ALL THAT.

06:50.143 --> 06:51.945
Sandy: I DON'T WANT
TO GO DOWN THERE. IT'S DARK.

06:51.979 --> 06:54.047
Fuck me!
HEY, MOM!

06:54.081 --> 06:56.149
YOU NEED SOME STICK 'N' CLICK
LIGHTS ON THESE STAIRS.

06:56.183 --> 06:59.119
THEY'RE ONLY $9.95 FOR A PACKAGE
OF THREE AT THE TARGET.

06:59.152 --> 07:01.054
WHY ARE WE ALL
UNDERGROUND?

07:01.088 --> 07:03.491
UH, GRANDMA,
THIS IS BRYCE.

07:03.524 --> 07:05.726
YOUR HAIRCUT LOOKS STRANGE
ON A GIRL.

07:05.759 --> 07:07.194
GO TO HELL,
PRUNE FACE.

07:07.227 --> 07:09.730
HEY, MA, WE GOT US
A LITTLE SITUATION DOWN HERE.

07:09.763 --> 07:10.731
I BROUGHT YOU
A FRUITCAKE.

07:10.764 --> 07:12.199
YOU SURE DID.

07:12.232 --> 07:14.502
OH, I GET IT --
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT ME.

07:14.535 --> 07:15.536
Kate: HELLO?

07:15.569 --> 07:16.670
Max: DOWNSTAIRS.

07:16.704 --> 07:18.038
IS THAT A PENIS?

07:18.071 --> 07:20.173
OH, BARELY.

07:20.207 --> 07:21.909
