BOXES OF GUNS AND PORNOGRAPHY?

07:28.982 --> 07:30.851
THEY'RE NOT MINE.

07:30.884 --> 07:32.486
THAT'S WHAT YOU
SAID WHEN I FOUND THE
MARIJUANA IN YOUR PANTS.

07:32.520 --> 07:33.887
EXCUSE ME?

07:33.921 --> 07:38.859
Marshall: KATE,
YOU MET GRANDMA SANDY?

07:38.892 --> 07:41.529
OH, WOW.
YEAH, SORTA.

07:41.562 --> 07:42.830
YOU SMELL GOOD.

07:42.863 --> 07:44.565
FUCK OFF!

07:44.598 --> 07:46.199
