A WHILE LONGER, MAX.

07:49.002 --> 07:49.970
DID SHE SAY "JIZZ"?

07:50.003 --> 07:51.071
UNFORTUNATELY.
YEP.

07:51.104 --> 07:52.740
Max:
OKAY, GUYS, LOOK.

07:52.773 --> 07:54.842
I KNOW IT SEEMS LIKE
THINGS ARE OUT OF CONTROL,

07:54.875 --> 07:56.644
BUT WE'RE GONNA GET
BACK ON TRACK, I PROMISE.

07:56.677 --> 07:58.746
WE JUST GOT TO --
GOT TO STICK TOGETHER

07:58.779 --> 08:00.280
LIKE A UNIT --
FAMILY UNIT.

08:00.313 --> 08:02.916
WE GOT TO KEEP REMEMBERING
TO HAVE NORMAL FAMILY FUN,

08:02.950 --> 08:05.619
DO NORMAL-FAMILY-FUN STUFF,
OKAY?

08:05.653 --> 08:07.120
NOW, YOUR MOM --
SHE'S COMING BACK,
JUST LIKE ALWAYS.

08:07.154 --> 08:09.089
GONNA TAKE SOME TIME.

08:09.122 --> 08:11.124
BUT THAT'S WHY WE'RE GONNA
TAKE HER TO HER FAVORITE PLACE.

08:11.158 --> 08:12.860
WE'RE GOING
TO THE ART MUSEUM.

08:12.893 --> 08:14.995
