08:15.028 --> 08:17.297
YEP.
UNFORTUNATELY.

08:17.330 --> 08:19.299
[ METAL CREAKING ]

08:19.332 --> 08:21.569
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

08:21.602 --> 08:23.737
