IS THIS "ART THERAPY"?

08:33.714 --> 08:35.683
AND IF SO,
IS IT WORKING AT ALL?

08:35.716 --> 08:38.586
SHUT THE FUCK UP,
NEIL.

08:38.619 --> 08:39.887
