JUST SIT HERE.

08:39.920 --> 08:41.221
WE SHOULD GO
TALK TO HER.

08:41.254 --> 08:42.222
HIM.

08:42.255 --> 08:43.791
Marshall: GO AHEAD.

08:43.824 --> 08:45.192
I'M HERE FOR SUPPORT,
BUT SERIOUSLY,

08:45.225 --> 08:46.894
