PSYCHIATRIC CARE.

09:00.874 --> 09:02.242
IT'S A FANCY NUTHOUSE.

09:02.275 --> 09:04.177
IT'S A PLACE OF "HOPE,
HEALING, AND HAPPINESS."

09:04.211 --> 09:05.613
THINK ABOUT IT.

09:05.646 --> 09:06.914
