IN THERE.

09:06.947 --> 09:08.248
[ SIGHS ]
LET'S ASK KATE.

09:08.281 --> 09:09.750
KATE!

09:09.783 --> 09:10.918
I DON'T NEED
TO ASK KATE.

09:10.951 --> 09:11.919
