09:11.952 --> 09:13.053
NOTHING.

09:13.086 --> 09:14.622
DON'T YOU THINK
YOUR MOM

09:14.655 --> 09:16.123
WOULD ENJOY SOME QUIET TIME
AWAY FROM THE FAMILY?

09:16.156 --> 09:17.825
I WOULD.

09:17.858 --> 09:19.860
SHE DOESN'T NEED QUIET TIME
AWAY. SHE NEEDS HELP.

09:19.893 --> 09:20.961
THAT'S WHAT I'M SAYING.

09:20.994 --> 09:21.962
OUR HELP. MY HELP.

09:21.995 --> 09:22.963
PROFESSIONAL HELP.

09:22.996 --> 09:24.297
I'M NOT PUTTING HER

09:24.331 --> 09:28.268
