23:05.618 --> 23:07.620
FOOLS IN LOVE.

23:07.654 --> 23:09.155
GIVE ME THAT.

23:14.160 --> 23:16.429
FIRST LOVE, HUH?

23:16.463 --> 23:19.599
NEVER FORGET
YOUR FIRST LOVE --

23:19.632 --> 23:21.100
THEIR HANDS...

23:21.133 --> 23:22.669
THEIR LIPS...

23:22.702 --> 23:24.971
THEIR EYES...

23:25.004 --> 23:28.541
ALL MASHED UP
IN SOME SHITTY CAR.

23:28.575 --> 23:30.176
THAT'S HARD
TO FORGET, TOO.

23:30.209 --> 23:33.079
YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT LOVE IS.
YOU'RE SCARED OF IT.

23:33.112 --> 23:34.747
OOH!
AND YOU CAN'T BREATHE

23:34.781 --> 23:36.949
WITHOUT MAKING EVERYONE
AROUND YOU SCARED, TOO.

23:36.983 --> 23:39.786
WELL, I'M NOT SCARED OF YOU,
SO FUCK OFF.

23:42.522 --> 23:45.558
[ As Alice ] I KNOW
WHAT IT'S LIKE TO LOSE SOMEONE.

23:45.592 --> 23:47.126
I MISS DON VERY MUCH.

23:47.159 --> 23:51.097
IT WAS LIKE
LOSING A PIECE OF MYSELF.

23:51.130 --> 23:53.466
BUT THE HURT FADES.

23:53.500 --> 23:56.102
AND THE LOVE THAT YOU SHARED
WILL STAY IN YOUR HEART FOREVER.

23:56.135 --> 23:58.070
DOESN'T MATTER
HOW LONG YOU LOVED HIM

23:58.104 --> 23:59.906
OR HOW WELL
YOU THINK YOU DID IT --

23:59.939 --> 24:02.509
JUST THAT YOU LOVED HIM
WITH ALL YOUR HEART

24:02.542 --> 24:05.144
AND THE BEST YOU COULD.

24:05.177 --> 24:09.048
YOU'RE A WONDERFUL BOY,
MARSHALL.

24:09.081 --> 24:11.584
I'M SO VERY PROUD
OF YOU.

24:12.685 --> 24:13.820
[ As Bryce ] BOOM!

24:13.853 --> 24:16.155
[ Chuckling ]
OH, MY GOD.

24:16.188 --> 24:20.259
THAT HAS TO BE
MY FAVORITE EXECUTION BY FAR.

24:20.292 --> 24:22.529
WELL, ONE LEFT,
BITCH BOY,

24:22.562 --> 24:24.531
AND I THINK
YOU KNOW WHO THAT IS.

24:24.564 --> 24:26.132
I NEED
A FUCKING SANDWICH.

24:29.035 --> 24:30.770
GET OFF ME!

24:30.803 --> 24:32.204
FUCK YOU!

24:32.238 --> 24:34.641
[ GRUNTS ]

24:37.009 --> 24:38.745
YOU FUCKER!

24:42.582 --> 24:43.750
OH!

24:45.985 --> 24:47.954
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

24:53.993 --> 24:56.529
[ As Tara ]
I'M SORRY.

24:56.563 --> 25:00.533
[ Sobbing ]
OH, NO.

25:00.567 --> 25:02.869
OH, MY BABY.

25:02.902 --> 25:04.737
I'M SO SO--

25:04.771 --> 25:06.205
OH, GOD.

25:10.910 --> 25:13.212
[ SIGHS ]

25:13.245 --> 25:15.682
ORGANIC VEGGIES, HUH?

25:15.715 --> 25:17.817
AND TENNIS COURTS.

25:17.850 --> 25:20.119
'ROUND-THE-CLOCK
PSYCHIATRIC CARE.

25:20.152 --> 25:21.554
YEP.

25:25.091 --> 25:27.560
THINK IT'LL WORK
THIS TIME?

25:27.594 --> 25:29.161
I DON'T KNOW.

25:29.195 --> 25:31.030
NEW DRUGS,
NEW TREATMENTS.

25:31.063 --> 25:32.799
RIGHT.

25:32.832 --> 25:35.602
HEY, IT'S NOT FOR FOREVER.
IT'S JUST FOR NOW.

25:38.671 --> 25:41.107
I'LL MISS YOU.

25:41.140 --> 25:44.143
[ Chuckling ] WELL,
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

25:46.378 --> 25:49.749
FOR RICHER AND FOR POORER,
RIGHT?

25:49.782 --> 25:54.020
IN SICKNESS AND IN...

25:54.053 --> 25:55.254
HEALTH.

25:59.225 --> 26:00.359
MAX, STOP.

26:00.392 --> 26:01.594
WHAT?

26:01.628 --> 26:02.561
STOP.

26:08.668 --> 26:09.936
[ Voice breaking ]
I LOVE YOU.

26:09.969 --> 26:10.937
TARA.

26:10.970 --> 26:14.006
* IN THE DARK

26:14.040 --> 26:15.141
TA-- TARA!

26:15.174 --> 26:19.345
* WE HAVE NO BODIES

26:19.378 --> 26:21.047
FUCK!

26:21.080 --> 26:23.950
* WE HAVE NO WORRIES

26:23.983 --> 26:29.055
* WE HAVE NO LIMBS

26:29.088 --> 26:32.792
* IN THE DARK

26:32.825 --> 26:36.896
* CALLOUS FOOTSTEPS

26:36.929 --> 26:41.067
* TREAD THIN WATERS

26:41.100 --> 26:44.804
* SEA TO LAND

26:44.837 --> 26:48.808
* LET'S GET YOU SAFE NOW

26:48.841 --> 26:52.945
* LET'S GET YOU SAFE
NOW *

26:52.979 --> 26:56.248
* OH, COME AWAY
